14DH_METHOD *DH_meth_new(const char *name, int flags)
15{
16 DH_METHOD *dhm = OPENSSL_zalloc(sizeof(*dhm));
17
18 if (dhm != NULL) {
19 dhm->flags = flags;
20
21 dhm->name = OPENSSL_strdup(name);
22 if (dhm->name != NULL)
23 return dhm;
24
25 OPENSSL_free(dhm);
26 }
27
28 DHerr(DH_F_DH_METH_NEW, ERR_R_MALLOC_FAILURE);
29 return NULL;
30}

40DH_METHOD *DH_meth_dup(const DH_METHOD *dhm)
41{
42 DH_METHOD *ret = OPENSSL_malloc(sizeof(*ret));
43
44 if (ret != NULL) {
45 memcpy(ret, dhm, sizeof(*dhm));
46
47 ret->name = OPENSSL_strdup(dhm->name);

49 return ret;
50
51 OPENSSL_free(ret);
52 }
